Body xml document

Source: R/read_docx.R
docx_body_xml.Rd

Get the body document as xml. This function is not to be used by end users, it has been implemented to allow other packages to work with officer.

Usage

docx_body_xml(x)

Arguments

x

an rdocx object

Examples

doc <- read_docx()
docx_body_xml(doc)
